    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Fluent C++ builder for <ref refid="struct_f_tryll_graph_description" kindref="compound">FTryllGraphDescription</ref>. Typed AddXxx methods are declared in <ref refid="_tryll_graph_builder_8_nodes_8h_source" kindref="compound">TryllGraphBuilder.Nodes.h</ref> (generated). Not a USTRUCT — for programmatic C++ use only.</para>
<para>Example: UTryllGenerateParams* P = UTryllNodeParamsFactory::MakeGenerateParams(this); P-&gt;ModelName = TEXT(&quot;qwen2.5-0.5b-instruct&quot;); P-&gt;SystemPrompt = TEXT(&quot;You are helpful.&quot;);</para>
<para>// Protocol v2: wiring lives on each node&apos;s params (e.g. P-&gt;DefaultExit). <ref refid="struct_f_tryll_graph_description" kindref="compound">FTryllGraphDescription</ref> Graph = <ref refid="struct_f_tryll_graph_builder" kindref="compound">FTryllGraphBuilder()</ref> .AddGenerate(TEXT(&quot;gen&quot;), P) // P-&gt;DefaultExit defaults to &quot;&quot; = END .SetStartNode(TEXT(&quot;gen&quot;)) .Build(); </para>
    </detaileddescription>
